---
---
<section class="section about-section" id="about">
    <div class="section-container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-tag frosted-glass">
                <span class="section-tag-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M12 2L14.85 9.15L22 12L14.85 14.85L12 22L9.15 14.85L2 12L9.15 9.15L12 2Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                เกี่ยวกับฉัน
            </span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Who is Sora?</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-text-col">
                <div class="about-text-card frosted-glass">
                    <h3 class="about-greeting">
                        <span>ฉันน่าจะชื่อ </span>
                        <span class="highlight">Sora</span>
                        <span> มั้ง</span>
                    </h3>
                    <p class="about-description">โผมมเป็น Content Creator สาย Tech บางครั้งโผมมมจะมาสอนใช้ software บางครั้งมาทำคลิป โชว์ Linux rice / Custom rom</p>
                    <p class="about-description">ทำคอนเท้นตามเวลาที่ว่าง</p>
                    <div class="about-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-icon">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="m16 13 5.223 3.482a.5.5 0 0 0 .777-.416V7.934a.5.5 0 0 0-.777-.416L16 11"></path>
                                    <rect x="2" y="6" width="14" height="12" rx="2"></rect>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="stat-info">
                                <span class="stat-label">Platform</span>
                                <span class="stat-value">Multi-Platform</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-icon">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="stat-info">
                                <span class="stat-label">สไตล์</span>
                                <span class="stat-value">ลองไปเรื่อย</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-icon">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="stat-info">
                                <span class="stat-label">สถานะ</span>
                                <span class="stat-value">Hackathon phase 1</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
